org.apache.taverna.visit

Interface Visitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the objects being visited.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HealthChecker<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataflowActivityHealthChecker, DisabledActivityHealthChecker, RemoteHealthChecker, StringConstantActivityHealthChecker, UnrecognizedActivityHealthChecker

    public interface Visitor<T>
    A Visitor can perform a visit of a VisitKind on a object. It can return a VisitReport giving details of the result of the visit, A Visitor may be time consuming, in which case it is only performed upon user request.
    Author:
    alanrw

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Returns true if the visitor can visit the specified object.

      An indication if the visit would take sufficient time that it should only be run upon user request
